David Duane Watson has been charged with the murder of his ex-wife Linda Watson and her mother-in-law Marilyn Cox . 
  Linda Watson was reported missing in August 2000 after she failed to pick up her daughter Jordynn from her ex-husband's home . 
  Police say she was killed during a custody dispute over the girl in 2003 . 
  Cox and her neighbor Renee Farnsworth were shot dead in the driveway of Linda Watson's home three years later . 
  Watson was arrested Saturday and charged with all three murders . 
 